@startuml Sequence_CreateGeofence
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10

title Sequence Diagram: Pembuatan Geofence

participant "User\n(Frontend)" as User
participant "Frontend\n(Vue.js)" as FE
participant "Leaflet.js\nMap" as Map
participant "Backend API\n(Express)" as BE
participant "Middleware\nAuth" as Auth
participant "Controller" as Controller
participant "MongoDB" as DB

User -> FE: 1. Buka halaman\nGeofences
FE -> BE: GET /api/geofences\n(dengan JWT Token)
activate BE
  Auth -> Auth: Verifikasi JWT\ntoken validity
  auth Auth -> DB: Jika valid,\nquery geofences
  DB --> Auth: Return data
  Auth --> BE: Token valid
  BE --> FE: Return geofences list
deactivate BE

FE -> Map: Render map dengan\nexisting geofences

User -> FE: 2. Klik tombol\n"Create New Geofence"
FE -> FE: Tampilkan form input:\n- Geofence name\n- Description\n- Toggle drawing mode

User -> Map: 3. Gambar polygon\npada map dengan\nclick-click koordinat

Map -> FE: 4. Return polygon\ncoordinates array

FE -> FE: Validasi:\n- Minimal 3 titik\n- Geofence name tidak kosong

User -> FE: 5. Klik tombol\n"Save Geofence"

alt Validasi Gagal
  FE -> FE: Tampilkan error message
else Validasi Sukses
  FE -> BE: POST /api/geofences\nPayload:\n- name\n- description\n- coordinates (GeoJSON)
  activate BE
    Auth -> Auth: Verifikasi JWT\ntoken
    Auth --> BE: Token valid,\nuserID valid

    Controller -> Controller: Parse GeoJSON\nPolygon
    Controller -> Controller: Validasi\ngeometry format

    Controller -> DB: Insert geofence\ndokumen baru
    activate DB
      DB -> DB: Create:\n{\n  userId,\n  name,\n  geometry (GeoJSON),\n  isActive: true,\n  createdAt\n}
      DB --> Controller: Return\n_id + data
    deactivate DB

    BE --> FE: Response 201 Created\n{\n  success: true,\n  message: "Geofence created",\n  geofence: {...}\n}
  deactivate BE

  FE -> FE: Tampilkan success\nmessage
  FE -> Map: Render geofence baru\ndi map
  FE -> FE: Refresh geofences\nlist di sidebar
end

note over FE, Map
  Koordinat dikumpulkan dengan:
  - Klik pada map untuk menambah point
  - Double-click untuk selesai
  - Format: [longitude, latitude]
  - GeoJSON Polygon format
end note

note over Controller
  Validasi di backend:
  - User hanya bisa lihat/buat
    geofence miliknya sendiri
  - Geometry harus valid GeoJSON
  - Closed polygon (first = last point)
end note

note over DB
  MongoDB GeoJSON format:
  {
    type: "Polygon",
    coordinates: [[
      [lon1, lat1],
      [lon2, lat2],
      [lon3, lat3],
      [lon1, lat1]  // Closed
    ]]
  }
end note

@enduml
